summary: Just the corset from Ashara Romantic Outfit for CBBE
descriptionHtml:
First off,  Thanks to SydneyB aka Ashara for the open license on these assests.  YAY!

The corset comes in two forms.
the body slot version
and an add on version that can be equipped with an armor (slot 57, i think)

it does not include the lace part or the skirt, but if people really want the lace I can add it and the skirt as an add on.  just ask in the comments section.

If you like this enough to endorse please endorse here http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/5577
I just did the easy part.

The corset is fitted for standard cbbev3.

have fun and thanks again SydneyB aka Ashara :)
author: SydneyB aka Ashara
